name: Eyes on the back
description: Eyes on the back... Eyes on the back of our grandfathers, they don't see through the blind lenses of today's screens. If only girls could see that their ambitions, such as pet names, are a way of getting by, and not a way of turning a profit. If only TV viewers could see that dancing is for fools, and not a way of getting the goods. If only the racing drivers could see that their cars are getting too slow, and need tuning, they coughed up a few gasses and volunteered some advice. But the girls still refuse to learn and continue to ride the crest of the fevered wave, never knowing that the water's poisoned and that the frog is living in their soup.
